	<h4><a href="www.servletsuite.com"><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=52a4e8430e102c26886b3e2a3272e2af&amp;size=100&amp;default=http%3A%2F%2Fcloud.24ways.org%2Fimg%2Fgravatar.png" class="gravatar" alt="" height="100" width="100" /> Dan Novik <small>www.servletsuite.com</small></a></h4>
