	<p>Thanx a lot!</p>

	<p>I&#8217;ve added:<br /><br /><code>document.getElementById(obj.id+'_edit').focus();</code><br /><br />at the end of the <code>edit</code>-function to focus on that field, maybe handy for other users..</p>
